<template>
  <v-dialog
      v-model="getShow"
      max-width="290"
    >
      <v-card>
        <v-card-title class="text-h5">
          Use Google's location service?
        </v-card-title>

        <v-card-text>
          Let Google help apps determine location. This means sending anonymous location data to Google, even when no apps are running.
        </v-card-text>

        <v-card-actions>
          <v-spacer></v-spacer>

          <v-btn
            color="green darken-1"
            text
            @click="backOpenGallery"
          >
            Disagree
          </v-btn>

          <v-btn
            color="green darken-1"
            text
            @click="backOpenGallery"
          >
            Agree
          </v-btn>
        </v-card-actions>
      </v-card>
    </v-dialog>
</template>

<script>
export default {
    name: 'ImageGallery',
    props: {
      showDialog: {
        type: Boolean,
        required: true,
      }
    },
    data() {
      return {
       show: false,
      }
    },
    computed:{
      getShow(){
        let localShow = this.showDialog
        return localShow
      }
    },
    methods: {
      backOpenGallery(){
        this.$emit('backOpenGallery',false)
      }
    },
    
}
</script>

<style>

</style>
